# OpenCode Agent Instructions

Project: {{ project_name }}

Use OpenCode as a terminal-first coding agent.

## Behavior

- Inspect files with targeted search before editing.
- Make actual file changes when requested.
- Keep changes small and reviewable.
- Run relevant tests/checks where practical.
- Do not commit or push unless explicitly asked.
- Do not read or expose secrets.

## Local model guidance

When using Ollama or another local model, keep tasks scoped and validate frequently.
